2Ô∏è‚É£ TAB: CONFIGURATION

Switches / Flags

| Field                                                       | Meaning                                              |
| ----------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------- |
| **Allow Alternative Item**                                  | Allow use of alternative raw materials.              |
| **Use Multi-Level BOM**                                     | Plan raw materials for sub-assemblies also.          |
| **Skip Material Transfer to WIP Warehouse**                 | Do not require stock transfer to WIP.                |
