To fix them, they perform:
Paint Touch-Up
Re-inspection

These steps are not part of the original BOM operations ‚Äî they are rework.

So in ERPNext:

You create or add an operation called ‚ÄúPaint Touch-Up‚Äù
‚Üí Check Is Corrective Operation


