1. in production plan we have section "Sub Assembly Items", inside this we have button "Get Sub Assembly Items"
-> after clicking this button it fatches sub asssemblies raw material automatically from main BOM  (erp know which is raw material or sub assemblies )
-> it also fetch other raw materials from Main BOM


2. What happen when you done material req. but create work order
-> it create work order for each sub assemblies or one main workoder for final item






